item.description:
Synopsis - Descendants (2015)
In an idyllic kingdom, the benevolent son of King Beast and Queen Belle ascends to the throne and gives the children of Cruella, Maleficent, the Evil Queen and Jafar a chance to redeem themselves. They will have to go to school with the heroes' children and face a dilemma: follow in their parents' footsteps and try to gain power or accept their innate goodness and help save the kingdom.
Click to expand...
Synopsis - Descendants 2 (2017)
When the pressure of belonging to royalty becomes too much for Mal, she returns to her rotten roots on the Isle of the Lost. There, she discovers that her archenemy Uma, Ursula's daughter, has taken her place as the self-proclaimed queen of the ruined city. Uma leads her band of pirates to break through the barrier between the island of Los Perdidos and Auradon.
Click to expand...
Synopsis - Descendants 3 (2019)
Mal, Evie, Carlos and Jay return to the Isle of the Lost to recruit a new group of villains and bring them to Auradon Prep. When a breach in the barrier puts Auradon at risk, Mal decides to close it permanently for fear that Uma and Hades want revenge on the kingdom. Despite this, a dark force threatens the people of Auradon, and it will be up to Mal and the VKs to save everyone in this epic battle.
